Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:17.70,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}我刚刚在计程车上 听过这个故事…{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ugh, I just heard this story in the cab...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:21.62,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}然后我就再也忘不了{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and it is all I can think about.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:26.80,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}太令人意外了 怎么…{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is amazing. I mean, how...?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:30.01,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}- 怎么会这样子的呢？ - 我们是在同一个研究所{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- How did this happen?     - Ross and I were in grad school together.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:33.60,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}毕业后就没见过面了 我一到中国{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We haven't seen each other since then. I land in China...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:35.60,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}你们猜负责的人是谁？{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}guess who's in charge of the dig?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:36.89,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}茱莉{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Julie!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:39.93,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}这不是太妙了吗？{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Julie. Isn't that great?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:45.15,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}真是妙得让人想踹你一脚 再对着你的脖子吐口水{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Isn't that just kick-you-in-the-crotch, spit-on-your-neck fantastic?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:49.28,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}只是一种形容的方式{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's an expression.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:52.45,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}我们只是很快的 来打声招呼{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We just wanted to say a quick hi.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:54.82,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}- 然后我们就要去看宝宝   - 然后睡一觉{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Then we're gonna go see the baby.     - Then get some sleep.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:57.49,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}现在其实是明晚六点钟 我们的时差{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yeah, it's 6:00 tomorrow night, our time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:05:01.03,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}好 千万别告诉我明天会怎样 因为我喜欢惊喜{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well don't tell us what's gonna happen, though Because I like to be surprised.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:07.71,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}- 再见    - 再见{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Bye!     - Bye.{\r}
