Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:20.68,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}- 当然好   - 谢谢{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Sure.     - Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:22.85,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}- 嘿 瑞秋…   - 你跟他说了没？{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Hey, Rach...     - Did you talk to him yet?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:24.36,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}- 没   - 那就甭想喝{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- No.     - Then, no.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:39.49,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}你在中国到底发生什么事了？{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, what the hell happened to you in China?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:42.58,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}上回我们离开这里的时候 你还爱着…{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I mean, when last we left you, you were in love with, you know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:45.08,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}我知道 曾经是那样没错{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I know. I know I was.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:47.84,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}可是我心中一直有个声音 在提醒我…{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But there was always this voice inside that kept saying:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:52.14,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}"那是不可能的 你要往前走" 你知道那是谁的声音吧？{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}"It's never gonna happen. Move on." You know whose voice that was?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:54.09,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}上帝吗？{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}God?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.80,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}是你啊 老兄{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It was you, pal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:05:59.64,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}也许是上帝在模仿我{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, maybe it was God doing me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:05.06,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}你说得没错 在她眼里我只是一个朋友  就这样{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You were right. She looks at me and sees a friend. That's all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:09.90,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}然后我就遇到茱莉 我们在一起很棒{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And then I met Julie, and... I don't know. We're having a great time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:14.61,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}要不是你的话 我绝对不可能跟她在一起的{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I never would have gone for it with her, if it hadn't been for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:18.41,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}嗯 你欠我一个大人情了  大个儿{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, you owe me one, big guy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:20.07,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}你的柠檬汁来了{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Here's your lemonade.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:21.33,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}我没叫啊{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I didn't order lemonade.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:26.20,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}那就拿回去还 不然他们会算钱的{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh. Well then you better go take that back. They're gonna charge you for that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:28.87,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}- 但…   - 快 快 快 快点 快点{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- But...     - Go, go, go! Come on, come on!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:33.13,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}好 你有什么发现？{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Okay, so, uh, what did you find out?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:37.01,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}他说…{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He said...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:44.18,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}- 他说他们在一起很棒 抱歉   - 什么？{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- He said they're having a great time. I'm sorry.     - What?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:47.90,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}不过 只要你愿意用心看待 还是有一线希望的{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the silver lining, if you wanna see it...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:51.31,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}也就是 这全是他自行决定的…{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is that he made this decision all by himself...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:54.57,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}绝对没有任何外来力量的协助{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}without any outside help whatsoever.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:57.78,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}这样怎么会叫一线希望呢？{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}How is that a silver lining?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:07:00.57,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}必须很用力 才能看到"一线"希望{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You have to really wanna see it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:09.00,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}讽刺的是 这些家伙都是上体育课时没人愿意挑的{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Ironically, these guys were picked last in gym.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:11.75,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}嘿 菲比{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hey, Pheebs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:14.76,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}- 知道我在想什么吗？ - 哦 可以{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- You know what I'm thinking?     - Oh, okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:20.31,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}在想…{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}How...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:23.22,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}你很久没跟人嘿咻了…{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it's been so long since you've had sex...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:26.51,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}所以你在想 现在有没有什么新花招？{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you're wondering if they've changed it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:30.40,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}不是 不过现在 我真的在想这件事了{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No. Although now that's what I'm thinking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:33.81,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}那你刚才在想什么？{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, what were you thinking?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:38.11,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}你帮他们剪了很棒的发型 我在想你也可以帮我剪{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I was thinking you gave the guys great haircuts. I thought you'd like to do mine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:40.03,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}哦 不要{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh! No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:44.33,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}- 有何不可？ - 因为我只是…{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Why not?     - Because I'm just...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:47.99,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}我是个控制狂 而且非常的挑剔{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm incredibly anal and an unbelievable control freak.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:51.76,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}- 不 你不是   - 我知道我不是 不过你是{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- No, you're not.     - I know I'm not, but you are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:55.13,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}我只是不想伤你的感情{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I was trying to spare your feelings.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:58.17,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}喂 嗨 你好{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hello? Oh, hi.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:08:01.06,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}好 罗斯 等一下 茱莉找你{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yeah, hold on a second. Ross, Julie for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:06.39,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}喂 嗨{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hello? Hi.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:09.72,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}嘿 有人认识什么好裁缝师吗？{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Hey. Anybody know a good tailor?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:11.98,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}- 有衣服要修改吗？ - 不是{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- You need clothes altered?     - No, no.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:15.40,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}我只是想找个人拿粉笔在我身上画{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I'm just looking for a man to draw on me with chalk.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:18.90,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}去找法兰克 我家的人总是找他{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Go see Frankie. My family's been going to him forever.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:23.58,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}我15岁时第一套西装就是他做的 不 等等 是16岁{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He did my first suit when I was 15. No, wait, 16.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:27.37,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}不 抱歉 是15岁{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, excuse me, heh, 15.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:30.84,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}好吧 1990年到底是什么时候？{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}All right, when was 1990?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:35.97,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}好吧 当棉花棒碰到东西 就别继续挖下去了{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Okay, you have to stop the Q-Tip when there's resistance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:47.39,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}好 好的 甜心 我们持会儿见了{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Okay. Okay. Sweetheart, I'll see you later.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:49.68,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}好的 拜 什么？{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Okay, bye. What?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:53.40,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}喔 你真甜{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Oh, that is so sweet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:56.36,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}不…{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No... Ha, ha.{\r}
