Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:29.69,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}巴洛和我并没有复合{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Paolo and I are not back together.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:31.95,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}那只是我干的一件傻事{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That was a stupid thing I did.{\r}
