Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.78,0:19:50.72,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}是否就像是 你跟一个人分手…{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is this one of those things where you break up with a guy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:55.18,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}然后我对你说出我的看法 然后你隔日就又跟他复合{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Then I tell you what I think... ...and the next day you get back together with him...{\r}
