Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:19:59.56,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}好吧{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:01.94,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}好 那么 我觉得那家伙是个大浑球{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Um, well, then, I think the guy's scum.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:06.56,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}我讨厌他 我真的… 真的很恨他{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I hate him. I mean, I actually... I physically hate him.{\r}
