Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:13.28,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}你太棒了 他配不上你{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And you are way too good to be with a guy like that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:15.74,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}- 真的？ - 瑞秋？{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}- Really?     - Rach?{\r}
