Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.10,0:20:30.76,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}你知道吗？ 就是一个会在每天醒来就想着…{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You know? Someone who wakes up every morning thinking:{\r}
