Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:40.02,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}就像我对茱莉的感觉一样{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Like the way I do with Julie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:48.27,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}还有什么"其次"的话吗？{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Was there a "second of all"?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:57.12,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}不 我想就这些了{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}No, um, I think that was the whole "all."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:00.96,Default01,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs20\fn华文楷体}我得走了 好吗？{\r}\N{\blur3\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I gotta go. Okay?{\r}
